José Baviera https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jos%C3%A9_Baviera 0 José Baviera (17 August 1906 – 13 August 1981) was a Spanish film actor. He appeared in more than 190 films and television shows between 1924 and 1979. He starred in Luis Buñuel's 1962 film The Exterminating Angel.
